'''Chewa''', wotchedwanso '''Nyanja''', ndi chinenero cha banja la chinenero cha Bantu. Chiwerengero cha chiwerengero cha maina chi- chigwiritsiridwa ntchito m'zinenero, choncho chinenerocho chimatchedwa Chichewa ndi Chinyanja (spelled Cinianja ku Mozambique). Ku Malawi, dzinali linasinthidwa mwachindunji kuchokera ku Chinyanja kupita ku Chichewa mu 1968 polimbikitsidwa ndi Pulezidenti [[Hastings Kamuzu Banda]] (mwiniwake wa fuko la Chewa), ndipo izi ndizimene zimagwiritsidwa ntchito masiku ano ku Malawi]]. Ku [[Zambia]], chiyankhulochi chimadziwika kuti Nyanja kapena Cinyanja / Chinyanja '(chinenero) cha m'nyanja' (kutanthauza [[Lake Malawi]]). Chewa ndi gulu la chinenero chimodzi (Guthrie Zone N) monga [[Tumbuka]], [[Sena]], ndi [[Nsenga]].

Chewa ndilo chinenero chodziwika kwambiri ku Malawi, chomwe chimayankhula makamaka m'madera akumidzi ndi akummwera a dzikoli. "Ndi chimodzi mwa zilankhulo zisanu ndi zi≈µiri za chiAfrika za Zambia, zomwe zimalankhulidwa makamaka ku Eastern Province. Zimalankhulanso ku Mozambique, makamaka m'madera a Tete ndi Niassa, komanso ku Zimbabwe komwe, malinga ndi ena Chiwerengerocho ndilo gawo lachitatu lomwe limagwiritsiridwa ntchito chinenero cha m'deralo, pambuyo pa Chichewa ndi Northern Northern Ndebele. " Ichi chinali chimodzi mwa zinenero 55 zomwe zikupezeka pa ndege ya Voyager spacecraft.

